name: Screen Rant
about:
Screen Rant debuted in 2003 and has grown into the largest source of breaking entertainment news and original features for movies, TV, comics, anime, and more.

Owned and operated by Valnet Inc. (Valnetinc.com), Screen Rant not only reports news but analyzes and editorializes it with unique insight that engages everyone from casual entertainment lovers to hardcore movie buffs. With television, film, comics, and video game news, reviews, podcasts, and a YouTube channel with over 10 million subscribers, Screen Rant is the ultimate geek entertainment destination.

For copyright matters relating to our channel please contact us directly at : legal@valnetinc.com
